  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This prospective cohort study of an almond-enriched diet (within the overall context of Asian
      Indian dietary guidelines) was conducted to test the hypothesis that in patients with T2DM
      almond-enriched balanced diet improves glycemic measures and CVD risk factors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
